content: /*<![CDATA[*/ $('#title').html($('meta[name=map-description]').attr('content')); /*]]>*/ Zero Trust Secure Access module for macOS version 2.20.68 June 2, 2025—The latest version of the Zero Trust Secure Access Module for macOS has been released. Enhancements Displays a system notification when Private Access is disconnected. Resolved issues After updates, Zero Trust Secure Access would still show the sign-in popup window. When Mac device was shut down and rebooted a few times, the Zero Trust Secure Access would display a blank UI. © 2025 Trend Micro Incorporated. All rights reserved.Search Knowledge Base
